title: Global Outbound Channels Details for a Managed Account

channel_limit.description: Integer value that indicates the number of allocatable global outbound channels that are allocated to the managed account. If the value is 0 then the account will have no usable channels and will not be able to perform outbound calling.

email.description: The email of the managed account.

id.description: The user ID of the managed account.

manager_account_id.description: The user ID of the manager of the account.

record_type.description: The name of the type of data in the response.
